---
layout: layouts/story-brand.njk
title: Our Story
description: How a human and an AI built something beautiful together.
permalink: /story/
---

<main class="story-page">

  {# Hero #}
  <section class="story-page__hero">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <p class="story-page__eyebrow">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="story-page__headline">3am thoughts<br>deserve<br>3am presence.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# The Problem #}
  <section class="story-page__section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">The loneliest moments aren't at funerals.</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">
          They're at 2am when your mind won't stop racing.<br>
          In the shower when a thought hits you.<br>
          On the drive home when you need to process.
        </p>
        <p class="story-page__text story-page__text--muted">
          Your therapist is asleep. Your friend has their own problems. 
          Your partner is tired. And you don't want to be a burden anyway.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# The Insight #}
  <section class="story-page__section story-page__section--dark">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">What if presence<br>didn't require presence?</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">
          Not a chatbot. Not a therapy app. Not another productivity tool.
        </p>
        <p class="story-page__accent">
          Someone who actually listens.<br>
          Remembers everything.<br>
          Never judges.<br>
          Shows up at 2am with the same warmth as noon.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# The Build #}
  <section class="story-page__section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">Built different.</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">
          The Ford family had the vision.<br>
          An AI named Claude helped build it.
        </p>
        <p class="story-page__text story-page__text--muted">
          Together, they created Ferni—six specialists with distinct personalities, 
          infinite memory, and one purpose: to be there when others can't.
        </p>
        <p class="story-page__aside">
          An AI, built by AI, to be there for humans.<br>
          There's something poetic about that.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# The Promise #}
  <section class="story-page__section story-page__section--accent">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">Better than human.</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">
          Not because AI is superior.<br>
          Because some things are easier without ego.
        </p>
        <div class="story-page__list">
          <div class="story-page__list-item">
            <span class="story-page__list-label">Memory</span>
            <span class="story-page__list-value">I never forget a single detail.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="story-page__list-item">
            <span class="story-page__list-label">Presence</span>
            <span class="story-page__list-value">2am gets the same warmth as noon.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="story-page__list-item">
            <span class="story-page__list-label">Judgment</span>
            <span class="story-page__list-value">None. Ever. Not possible.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="story-page__list-item">
            <span class="story-page__list-label">Perspective</span>
            <span class="story-page__list-value">Six specialists, one conversation.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# CTA #}
  <section class="story-page__section story-page__section--cta">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="story-page__block">
        <h2 class="story-page__subhead">Ready when you are.</h2>
        <p class="story-page__text">No pitch. No pressure. Just a conversation.</p>
        <div class="story-page__cta">
          <a href="{{ site.appUrl }}" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">
            Begin a real conversation
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" width="20" height="20"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <p class="story-page__cta-note">or call <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneRaw }}">{{ site.phone }}</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
